Note: Main Entry Point for Test Execution

Process called "main" that takes args as List[String] returns Integer:
    Print "🚀 Runa AI Decision System - Master Test Runner"
    Print "=============================================="
    Print ""
    
    Note: Parse command line arguments
    Let environment be if length of args > 0 then args[0] else "development"
    Let config be create_test_configuration with environment
    
    Note: Run comprehensive test suite
    Let test_suite be run_all_decision_tests with config
    
    Note: Return appropriate exit code
    If test_suite.tests_failed > 0:
        Return 1  Note: Tests failed
    Else:
        Return 0  Note: All tests passed

Note: Export main test runner functions
Process called "run_decision_tests_with_environment" that takes environment as String returns TestSuite:
    Let config be create_test_configuration with environment
    Return run_all_decision_tests with config

Process called "run_all_decision_tests_with_environment" that takes environment as String returns TestSuite:
    Note: Main entry point for external test runners
    Let config be create_test_configuration with environment
    Return run_all_decision_tests with config

Process called "run_quick_smoke_tests" returns TestSuite:
    Let config be create_test_configuration with "quick"
    Set config.performance_testing_enabled to false
    Set config.stress_testing_enabled to false
    Set config.timeout_per_test_ms to 10000
    Return run_all_decision_tests with config

Process called "run_full_production_tests" returns TestSuite:
    Let config be create_test_configuration with "production"
    Return run_all_decision_tests with config